Product description

Minlu 3-in-1 Multi USB Charging Cable 3.0A

The durability youve come to expect from Minlu 3-in-1 Charger Cordnow with universal compatibility. With iP, USB-C and Micro USB connectors built-in, its the only cable youll ever need. Support to charger most of the mobile phones available on market.

Features

Length: 120cm (4Ft)

Material: TPE + Aluminium Alloy

Packing: 2 3 in 1 Retractbale Multi USB Cables

Warm tips

The maximum total output current of iP is 2.4A, USB-C is 3.0A and Micro-USB is 2.4A (For total, not for each end)

The actual charging speed is determined by the highest output that the wall charger can provide, you can charge multiple devices at the same time with a 5V/2.4A3.0A wall charger, particularly suitable for family or guests.

4Ft/120cm and 3 in 1 Retractable Design

4Ft/120cm is perfect length for long distance charging, 3-in-1 retractable design, makes the cord portable and only need one cable when you are on a business trip or traveling.

3-in-1 Retractable Multiple Charging Cables

USB 2.0: Universally compatible for iPhone, Micro-USB & Type-C devices, it has 3 different ports to USB cable for your most needs, it can charge 3 devices at the same time.

iOS-Ports: With charging and data transmission functions. Compatible with iPhone 14 Plus/ 14 13 12 11 Pro Max/ 14 13 12 11 Pro/ 14 13 12 Mini/ SE/ 14 13 12 11/ XS/ XS Max/ XR/ 8/ 8 Plus/ 7/ 7 Plus/ 6s/ 6s Plus/ 6 Plus/ 6/ 5/ 5S, Pad Air/ Air 2, Pad Pro, Pad mini Pod touch.

Type-C: Have charge function. Compatible with iPhone 17 Air/ 17 16 15 Pro Max/ 17 16 15 Pro/ 16 15 Plus/ 17 16 15, Samsung Galaxy UItra S25 S24 S23 S22 S21 S20 S10 S9 S8, Note 10 9 8 7, New Book 2015, Book Pro 2016, ChromeBook Pixel 2015, Google Nexus 6P/5X, OnePlus 2/3/4/5, Huawei ,Moto z force,Moto z2 play/Google Pixel/XL/2/2 XL and more.

Micro-USB: Have charge function. Compatible with most Android and Windows phones, tablets and many other devices including HTC/Nokia/LG/Sony/Bluetooth Speakers/Headphone/Earphone/MP4/MP3/PS/GPS device.

Charging Fast 3.0A & Syncing

The thicker copper core wire inside can realize faster and more stable charging, which is 35% faster than ordinary multi cables.

Only iOS connector support data transmission, 480 Mbps.

Flexible And Durable

Withstand 12,000+ bending.

How to use?

Please pull both side at the same time!!!

Please pull both side at the same time!!!

Please pull both side at the same time!!!

Simplify your life with MINLU retractable multi charger cable

Organize Your Environment: Bid farewell to cable clutter and untidy desks. Maintain a clean and organized workspace by charging multiple devices using a single cable.

NOTE: When charging multiple devices simultaneously, please use a 5V/3.0A (9V/2.0A) or 60W adapter.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

5 out of 5 stars
Decent Multi Charging Cord for Everyday Use
Ive been using this multi charging cable for some time, and it has been generally useful. It combines different connectors in one cable, which helps reduce the number of cords I need to keep around. The retractable feature is practical and keeps it from getting tangled. It fits easily in a drawer or bag and is simple to store. I use it for my phone and other small devices, and it works as expected. The charging speed is reasonable, and I havent noticed any major problems. The cables seem to be made fairly well and have held up to regular use so far. Both cables in the pack function the same, and the retraction works fine. It has been convenient to have around the house and in the car. Its also helpful when someone else needs to charge a different type of device. The length is adequate and works for most situations. It hasnt shown signs of wear yet, which is a good sign. It charges steadily without getting warm. Id say its a decent cable for the price. Overall, it does the job without any issues, and Im satisfied with it.

    The 3-in-1 design offers three different connectors - USB Type-C, Micro USB, and Lightning - all in one cable.
